<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>非零环绕规则</title>
</head>
<body>
	<canvas id="canvas" width="800" height="500"></canvas>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		var canvas = document.getElementById('canvas'),
			context = canvas.getContext('2d');
		context.fillStyle = '#ff0000';
		// true 顺时针绘制图形，false 逆时针绘制图形
		context.arc(400,250,200,0,2*Math.PI,false);
		context.arc(400,250,160,0,2*Math.PI,true); //false
		context.fill();
	</script>
</body>
</html>
